WEBVTT

00:04:58.434 --> 00:05:02.006
They should create a sense of curiosity.

00:05:02.879 --> 00:05:05.640
This is the way to create
a cultural place.

00:05:05.664 --> 00:05:09.523
Curiosity is the beginning
of a cultural attitude.

00:05:10.188 --> 00:05:13.722
And there's a piazza there,
you can see that piazza.

00:05:14.379 --> 00:05:19.593
And a piazza is the beginning
of urban life.

00:05:19.617 --> 00:05:22.363
A piazza is the place where people meet.

00:05:22.387 --> 00:05:24.396
And they mix experience.

00:05:25.823 --> 00:05:27.455
And they mix ages.

00:05:28.815 --> 00:05:32.965
And, you know, in some way,